  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face an onslaught of demonic hordes and survive through inferno in Hell Survivors. Create powerful builds from a variety of heroes, weapons, and special abilities in order to survive for 20 minutes. Are you strong enough to come back from purgatory, or will you allow the nightmare creatures to consume you? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Challenging runs of 20 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fast paced, skill based shooter mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic build system with stats upgrades, abilities and equipment </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock new levels, heroes, weapons and equipment trough a meta progression system </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Diverse bosses and elite enemies featuring unique mechanics and attack patterns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Stunning dark stylized art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Thrilling post-metal adaptive soundtrack  </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face an onslaught of demonic hordes and survive through inferno in Hell Survivors. Create powerful builds from a variety of heroes, weapons, and special abilities in order to survive for 20 minutes. Are you strong enough to come back from purgatory, or will you allow the nightmare creatures to consume you? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Challenging runs of 20 minutes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fast paced, skill based shooter mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic build system with stats upgrades, abilities and equipment </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock new levels, heroes, weapons and equipment trough a meta progression system </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Diverse bosses and elite enemies featuring unique mechanics and attack patterns</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Stunning dark stylized art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Thrilling post-metal adaptive soundtrack  </p></li></ul>",
